snippet.title: Wingspan: Oceania Expansion - Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
In Wingspan: Oceania Expansion, the second DLC to Wingspan, we discover the awe-inspiring birds of Oceania! The DLC includes new gameplay features, an additional resource - nectar, 95 extraordinary bird cards, an alternative player board and more!

Available soon on Steam, GOG, Android, iOS, Nintendo Switch and Xbox.

To learn more follow our social media:

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MonsterCouchGames
Twitter: https://twitter.com/monstercouch
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/monstercouchgames/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@monstercouch

Wingspan Discord: https://discord.gg/wingspan
Official Wingspan Page: https://www.monstercouch.com/wingspan/oceania-expansion/
